
Title: Spring Boot connect MySQL
SubTitle: Spring Boot MySQL database connect by JPA with hibernate

---------------------------------------------------------------------

step1: Create spring boot gradle project
https://start.spring.io/

step2: Import SpringMySQLJpa project in IntelliJ IDEA

step3: Create sub packages for project structure
config, ctrl, model, repo, service

step4: Add annotation in main class for initialize component, entity and repository
@ComponentScan("com.example.SpringMySQLJpa")
@EntityScan("com.example.SpringMySQLJpa.model")
@EnableJpaRepositories(basePackages = {"com.example.SpringMySQLJpa.repo"})

step5: Create/Add model(s)

step6: Create repository for model

step7: Create service interface and implementable class for controller and repository
		and create controller for User

step8: Configure application yml file for MySQL

step10: Now run the project ... and add some data in User table

step11: now test the project from browser


